CHECKLIST

- make a backup of the old version

- write a news announcing the changes from the old to the current version

- make a new src

mkdir /usr/share/gs/soft/oz-xxx
cd $!
cvs get -l Oz
cvs get Oz/lib
cvs get Oz/bin
cvs get Oz/elisp
cvs get Oz/include
cvs get Oz/Emulator
cvs get Oz/Compiler
cvs get Oz/demo
cvs get Oz/Tools
cvs get Oz/ozwish

- install bin/ozplatform in your PATH

- edit Imake.tmpl:
    OZVERSION: make a unique version number
    OZHOME: target directory for installation

- edit Compiler/Imake.tmpl
    SPLIB : sicstus prolog

- edit Compiler/backend/Imakefile

- edit ozwish/Imakefile
    OZWISHHOME

- ./ozmkmf

- make World
   make Makefiles
   make all
        include
        Emulator
        Compiler/backend
        Compiler/frontend
        lib
                make unixo

   make install
        bin
        elisp
        ozwish
        Emulator
        Compiler/backend
        Compiler/frontend
        lib
        lib/unix.o
        demo
        demo/documentation (copy !)

        make install SUBDIRS= (ANNOUNCE, README, ...)

- test your installation:

   $(OZHOME)/bin/oz

- create a new entry in /usr/share/gs/bin/scripts/oz-wrapper

- mkdir dist
- make dist
